# Restricted or private data must never be committed.
data/raw/
data/restricted/
data/private/
restricted/
private/
raw/
secrets/
credentials/

# Real station/site artifacts and row-level outputs are blocked by default.
*real*
*restricted*
*station_coordinates*
*station_coords*
*site_coordinates*
*site_coords*
*latitude*
*longitude*
*latlon*
*lonlat*
*真实*
*站点*
*坐标*

